snippet.title: Loadout and Progression | Wardens Rising Dev Diary #3
snippet.description:
Greetings, Wardens! Welcome to our third Dev Diary! 

In this episode, we'll dive into the game flow and some mechanics for upgrading your characters and progressing through the game. 

Wishlist Wardens Rising on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1055560/Wardens_Rising/

Don't forget to leave a like and subscribe to our channel!

Twitter: https://x.com/wardensrising

Discord: https://discord.gg/6QwU7c8JQ9

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/user/WardensRising/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wardensrising
